@harrisdemocrats (2/3) Here is my plan on common-sense gun control: 

Introduce legislation to regulate magazine size. 

Introduce legislation to ban assault and most semi-automatic weapons, with an exemption for agricultural uses because of Texas’ feral hog problem.

We will rebuild our neighborhoods and ensure everyone is taken care of — like Texans always do.

